body_html:
The new zip file doesn't contain the graph. I think the graph you need is the one in https://github.com/tensorflow/models/inception.

As soon as feasible, we should migrate all these examples to use SavedModel, which would contain both the graph, the checkpoint, and also annotations to say which tensors to feed and fetch.

body:
The new zip file doesn't contain the graph. I think the graph you need is the one in https://github.com/tensorflow/models/inception. 

As soon as feasible, we should migrate all these examples to use SavedModel, which would contain both the graph, the checkpoint, and also annotations to say which tensors to feed and fetch.
